<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><p>Spring Security 2.0.0 RC1 is now available.<br> <a target="_blank" href="https://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=73357&amp;package_id=270072&amp;release_id=588844"><br>Download</a> | <a target="_self" href="http://jira.springframework.org/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=10040&amp;styleName=Html&amp;version=10651">Changelog</a> | <a target="_self" href="http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=51953">Announcement</a><br> <br> Over 65 issues have been addressed, including OpenID integration, a new "protect-pointcut" for AspectJ expressions, dynamic retrieval of method authorization metadata, support for method authorization on all method types (interface, class, bridge, generic, superclass), restful URI authorization, namespace improvements, dependency updates and much more!<br></p>
</div>
